OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FWindy
OL,6,Fon Wednesday with some warm sunshine,
OL,7,Fthough possible showers overnight.
OL,8,FMostly fine thereafter with sunny
OL,9,Fperiods and turning warmer with winds
OL,10,Fslowly easing. Chilly nights with
OL,11,Frural frosts possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
